<p>Gas dryers are relatively uncommon in Parkdale compared to some other Toronto neighbourhoods, but they do exist in some of the larger Victorian homes that have natural gas service. Gas dryer igniter failure is the most common gas-specific repair call — the igniter glows but doesn't reach the temperature needed to open the gas valve, or it cracks and fails completely. Our technicians are licensed for gas appliance repair and carry igniters for the most common Whirlpool, Maytag, and GE gas dryer models.</p>
